<font color="#FF0000">THE BOOK SAYS.........</font><br>
<tt>Mon Nov  3  3:36:22 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I'm getting a little tired of this moot point..&quot;what if..shit!&quot;<br>
If frogs had wings they wouldn't bump their asses all the time!<br>
The Damn war is a done deal..all the speculation on why it happened is secondary in importance to the fact that it did happen.  There's walking wounded all over the place who need help.  After the fist fight, I don't want to hear some tired tirade about who started it.  I want some broken noses and busted knuckles tended to.<br>
This global, holistic, politically correct, save the whale bullshit is about to wear me out!<br>
I recognize the need to know history...it is some of the best fiction ever written.<br>
George Custer was a stupid, rotten, low down son of a bitch who was power crazy.<br>
This wonderful government that I fought for in Vietnam is the same machine that justified stealing the lands of my ancestors...lies then...lies now.  Today, greedy politicians are trying to undo the few treaties that weren't broken years ago.<br>
The Veterans Administration is a self serving bunch of lazy federal employees who's main concern is to deny the veteran his benefits so that they can get more salary and union benefits.  They hire a bunch of third world doctors who can't get certified in any state of the United States. Not only do they not know shit all about medicine...they can't speak English.  How did all this come about?  Give me a break...there would have been no Wounded Knee if this crooked government would have kept its promise back then.  There's that troublesome &quot;if&quot; word again.  Problem is.. they were liars then and they are liars now.<br>
Ignorant, greedy, deceitful, religiously fanatic, bastards understand one thing...death!  Too bad you have to kill a lot of innocent dumbasses before you get to the bad boys!<br>
I honor the Flag, and the concept of the United States on paper, and the people who have died and fought for that.. but I have lost almost all respect for two faced..smiling.. draft dodging trash that runs this country.<br>
When we broke from England we need some instant heroes... a sort of nucleus for nationalism to form around.  Henry Steele Commanger wrote &quot;Our Search for a Usable Past&quot; well we got with it and cranked out heroes at a pace that would rival Desert Storm (where everybody was a hero.. even the ones who did nothing but leave the U.S. to whore around in Germany for six months and never saw a grain of sand!)<br>
I don't fall for all the shit that has been written.. spent too much time in RVN, South America and other places doing shit that members of academic anonymous will never know or read about!<br><br>
I respect the articles and tidbits of information that attempt to explain the Vietnam War...respect the men and women dedicated to revealing truth.  I'm just fed up!<br><br>
Need to go away for awhile!  That's a historical fact!<br><br>
I honor warriors - MTF
